items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: +7% Chance to Block Attack Damage while affected by Determination
+8% chance to Evade Attack Hits while affected by Grace
110% increased Critical Strike Chance against Enemies on Consecrated Ground while affected by Zealotry
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.

items.name: Energised Armour
explicitMods: Increases and Reductions to Energy Shield in Radius are Transformed to apply to Armour at 200% of their value
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: "I've yet to see prayer stop an arrow."

items.name: Forbidden Flesh
explicitMods: Allocates Reigning Veteran if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flame
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The bodies of those wholly subsumed by the Tangle
continue to merge and mutate and cry out for release...

items.name: The Blue Nightmare
explicitMods: Gain 7% of Lightning Damage as Extra Chaos Damage

Passives granting Lightning Resistance or all Elemental Resistances in Radius
also grant Chance to Block Spell Damage at 50% of its value
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: and drown the undeserving beneath our might.

items.name: Forbidden Flame
explicitMods: Allocates Reigning Veteran if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flesh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire
continue to think and dream and beg for silence...
